Here is a little JS snippet you can adapt to filter the list down to remove the procedures not supported by a particular profile you want to view.<p><pre><code>    Array.prototype.filter.call(document.querySelectorAll(&quot;.disabled&quot;), function(v){return v.innerHTML === &quot;es2&quot;;}).forEach(function(v){v.parentElement.parentElement.removeChild(v.parentElement);});
</code></pre>
Notice the &quot;es2&quot;, that is where you select the profile.
